bonnie++: bonnie++ (Filesystem and disk benchmark & burn-in suite)
bonnie++:
bonnie++: bonnie++ filesystem and disk benchmark suite aggressively reads &
bonnie++: writes in various ways on your filesystem then outputs useful
bonnie++: benchmark performance data.  bonnie++ is also useful as a hardware,
bonnie++: disk, and filesystem stability test, exposing some types of hardware
bonnie++: or kernel failures that would otherwise be difficult to detect.
bonnie++:
bonnie++: http://www.coker.com.au/bonnie++/
bonnie++:
bonnie++: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
